## Intervals

Common monitoring intervals:
- `60` - Every minute
- `300` - Every 5 minutes (recommended)
- `600` - Every 10 minutes
- `900` - Every 15 minutes
- `1800` - Every 30 minutes
- `3600` - Every hour

